<emphasis id="B921AA6BFF952E2174BFCC7EFC33F932" box="[758,945,1661,1685]" italics="true" pageId="12" pageNumber="396">Pyrgulopsis rubra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="B921AA6BFF952E2175F0CC7DFB8EF931" bold="true" box="[953,1036,1662,1686]" pageId="12" pageNumber="396">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="A2121710FF952E2175F0CC7DFB8EF931" box="[953,1036,1662,1686]" pageId="12" pageNumber="396" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
A = portion of radular ribbon; B–C = central radular teeth; D = lateral teeth and inner marginal tooth; E = lateral, inner, and outer marginal teeth. Scale bars A = 20 µm; B–E = 10 µm.
